      <title>刺法论篇第七十二</title>
      <link>https://acuherb.xyz/posts/%E5%88%BA%E6%B3%95%E8%AE%BA%E7%AF%87%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%83%E5%8D%81%E4%BA%8C/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 12 Apr 2025 20:14:22 +0800</pubDate><author>124768092@qq.com (AcuHerb)</author>
      <guid>https://acuherb.xyz/posts/%E5%88%BA%E6%B3%95%E8%AE%BA%E7%AF%87%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%83%E5%8D%81%E4%BA%8C/</guid>
      <category domain="https://acuherb.xyz/categories/%E7%B4%A0%E9%97%AE/">素问</category>
      <description>探讨了人体内五行气机的升降变化及其对健康的影响，强调通过特定的针灸疗法来调整五脏气机的升降平衡，以预防和治疗因气机不顺导致的疾病。文章详细描述了各个脏腑在不同年运变化下的升降规律，并通过针灸调理来疏通气机、恢复气血平衡，防止疾病的发生。</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>气穴论篇第五十八</title>
      <link>https://acuherb.xyz/posts/%E6%B0%94%E7%A9%B4%E8%AE%BA%E7%AF%87%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%94%E5%8D%81%E5%85%AB/</link>
